<div class="title">Buzzing and Crashing</div>
<div class="substance">Rhodiola Rosea, Caffeine & Ginseng</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Evan&Exact=1">Evan</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Evan. "Buzzing and Crashing: An Experience with Rhodiola Rosea, Caffeine & Ginseng (exp53636)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Feb 24, 2007. erowid.org/exp/53636</div>

<br/>



